        <p>Absolutely! The Qure Micro-Infusion System is designed to be <strong>gentle and effective</strong> for most skin types, including sensitive skin.</p>
        <p>We know that everyone's skin is unique, and that's why our device is crafted to minimize irritation while maximizing results. </p>
        <p>The 24k gold plated micro-needles are <strong>designed to be virtually painless</strong>, and our serums are formulated to soothe and nourish even the most delicate skin.</p>
        <p>So, if you have sensitive skin, you can confidently use our Micro-Infusion System to achieve a <strong>healthier, more radiant complexion</strong>.</p>
